name: Untitled cat unboxing
description:
You're a robot and there's a cute cat.

But to reach it you must cross a maze, and you'll need to cooperate. With yourself. Your past self.

Controls
  • The usual four: Movement
  • Space: Clone yourself / Swap clone / Warp in time / Words cannot describe this
  • Escape: Exit
  • R: Restart level
Known issues

There are a lot of graphic bugs and glitches

Post-LD updates
  • Fixed a few of these glitches
